It doesn't hold up at all.

snippet.textDisplay: Yep. The whole way through the video, my thoughts were essentially that it doesn't matter if that's true at all, and it's an entertaining story either way. And really, why else would anyone make such a terrible tower other than to pull one over on someone, or make some weird architectural statement? Actually, I suppose the latter's possible, but most architectural statements are at least usable, even if they melt the occasional car dashboard.
